::DarkMouse::

She looked at Lightmare with surpize on her face.
"My what?  He's one of my commanders."
She just had her mind thrown for a loop.  Lightmare's question caught her 
totaly off gaurd.
"Yeah right, Quickstrike like me like that? You got to be kidding.  He has 
tons of other bot who are much better looking than I am.  Besides, he most 
likely hates me.  He's just putting up with me because Megatron ordered him 
to most likely."
She looked at Lightmare for a second.
"Do you like him? Are you wanting Quickstrike? Well, don't worry about me 
getting in the way.  I've got a snowball's chance in an inferno of getting 
Quickstrike to like me."
